channel.title: In need of help with my compiler... Yet again... (nice story to go with it too)
channel.description:
This is how it all started... So last summer I went on vacation to Africa with my Mom and Dad, while we were there we went on an exotic bush-walk, about halfway through our walk I decided to relieve my self on a near by tree, it was all going fine, then I happened to to notice an old temple to the right of me. Being the mighty courageous adventurer I am I set off to see what I could find. It was a magnificent temple that look as though is had been untouched for centuries. I then noticed there was something mounted onto the top of the temple, it was the mostly beautiful diamond I have ever layed my eyes on suddenly I found myself climbing the temple eager to get my hands on it, I ripped that diamond right off its mount and suddenly I heard a deathly screech! I quickly turned around to see a Arch Voodoo Priest gazing at me and chanting a ghastly verse, he then pulled from his pocket a necklace with seemed to be made out of human fingers (I'm not to sure) then he said to me 'May the almighty Baron Samedi have no mercy on our soul! be gone from our holy site and may all of your RuneScape Private Server compilers fail!'
So that's how it all started, and hopefully this is were it will end :\ I've been having compiler issues ever since last summer, I get them fixed, then they get them selves broken.
These are the only compiler issues I ever get so if someone could tell me the solutions to them, I will be free from my Voodoo curse.
[img]http://i723.photobucket.com/albums/ww237/Zezamu6/Compiler.jpg[/img]
[img]http://i723.photobucket.com/albums/ww237/Zezamu6/Untitled.jpg[/img]
Thank you very much in advance to anyone/s that can finally help me resolve these issues and I will rep blah blah blah :)
Cheers
